c0000000
00:00:01.590 --> 00:00:04.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- At last,
our second term has begun.</b></Default>

c0000001
00:00:04.420 --> 00:00:06.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>During summer break Mai
was completely booked up</b></Default>

c0000002
00:00:06.630 --> 00:00:08.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with her work.</b></Default>

c0000003
00:00:08.260 --> 00:00:10.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And her agency forbids us
from going on dates.</b></Default>

c0000004
00:00:11.140 --> 00:00:13.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Which means we barely saw
each other.</b></Default>

c0000005
00:00:13.260 --> 00:00:15.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Don't worry.
Once the second term starts,</b></Default>

c0000006
00:00:15.560 --> 00:00:17.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we'll see each other
at school all the time.</b></Default>

c0000007
00:00:18.100 --> 00:00:20.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- And those lonely days
have finally come to an end...</b></Default>

c0000008
00:00:21.610 --> 00:00:23.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is what I thought.</b></Default>

c0000009
00:00:23.770 --> 00:00:25.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's not a single Mai
to be seen.</b></Default>

c0000010
00:00:28.650 --> 00:00:30.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It doesn't look like she came
to school at all today.</b></Default>

c0000011
00:00:36.500 --> 00:00:37.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Come on, Mai.</b></Default>

c0000012
00:00:40.370 --> 00:00:42.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]
Mai!</b></Default>

c0000013
00:00:43.790 --> 00:00:44.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hmm?</b></Default>

c0000014
00:00:46.130 --> 00:00:47.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Who the hell are you?</b></Default>

c0000015
00:00:47.420 --> 00:00:49.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Huh?
- Come on, answer me.</b></Default>

c0000016
00:00:49.260 --> 00:00:50.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Who are you?</b></Default>

c0000017
00:00:51.470 --> 00:00:53.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Well, Mai, as you know,
I am the one you have a pure,</b></Default>

c0000018
00:00:54.050 --> 00:00:56.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>innocent relationship with--
Sakuta Azusagawa.</b></Default>

c0000019
00:00:56.390 --> 00:00:58.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [stammering]
Huh?</b></Default>

c0000020
00:00:58.640 --> 00:01:01.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's no way some guy
with dead-looking eyes like you</b></Default>

c0000021
00:01:01.140 --> 00:01:02.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is my sister's boyfriend.</b></Default>

c0000022
00:01:02.770 --> 00:01:04.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Sister?</b></Default>

c0000023
00:01:04.270 --> 00:01:05.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then who exactly are you?</b></Default>

c0000024
00:01:05.900 --> 00:01:07.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That would be Nodoka Toyohama.</b></Default>

c0000025
00:01:07.940 --> 00:01:09.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]
- And at least for now,</b></Default>

c0000026
00:01:09.950 --> 00:01:11.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm Mai Sakurajima.</b></Default>

c0000027
00:01:12.700 --> 00:01:15.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [groans]
I--It really is you.</b></Default>

c0000028
00:01:15.240 --> 00:01:16.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You know
from being stepped on?</b></Default>

c0000029
00:01:16.950 --> 00:01:18.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What kind of weird pervert
are you?</b></Default>

c0000030
00:01:18.700 --> 00:01:20.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- So what's going on, now?</b></Default>

c0000031
00:01:20.830 --> 00:01:22.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It's a dream, clearly.</b></Default>

c0000032
00:01:22.210 --> 00:01:23.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Except it isn't.</b></Default>

c0000033
00:01:23.670 --> 00:01:26.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When I woke up I had somehow
swapped bodies with her.</b></Default>

c0000034
00:01:26.170 --> 00:01:28.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Is it possible that
it could be--</b></Default>

c0000035
00:01:28.510 --> 00:01:30.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It's more than likely
puberty syndrome, yes.</b></Default>

c0000036
00:01:30.920 --> 00:01:32.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [exhales sharply]</b></Default>

c0000037
00:01:32.130 --> 00:01:33.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This again?</b></Default>

c0000038
00:01:34.680 --> 00:01:37.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [singing in Japanese]</b></Default>

c0000039
00:01:37.680 --> 00:01:40.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[The Peggies' "Kimi no sei"]</b></Default>

c0000040
00:01:40.640 --> 00:01:47.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

c0000041
00:02:22.930 --> 00:02:29.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

c0000042
00:02:49.250 --> 00:02:56.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

c0000043
00:03:04.060 --> 00:03:06.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[vacuum humming]</b></Default>

c0000044
00:03:08.770 --> 00:03:11.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Uh, Mai,
how much is the rent here?</b></Default>

c0000045
00:03:11.530 --> 00:03:12.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I don't pay rent.</b></Default>

c0000046
00:03:12.940 --> 00:03:14.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I bought the place.</b></Default>

c0000047
00:03:14.320 --> 00:03:15.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's your first time
at your girlfriend's home</b></Default>

c0000048
00:03:16.070 --> 00:03:17.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and that's your reaction?</b></Default>

c0000049
00:03:17.740 --> 00:03:19.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You should be happier.</b></Default>

c0000050
00:03:19.120 --> 00:03:21.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Maybe if the situation
wasn't what it is.</b></Default>

c0000051
00:03:21.790 --> 00:03:24.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- If it isn't a dream,
what are you saying it is?</b></Default>

c0000052
00:03:24.580 --> 00:03:26.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This can't be real!
There's no way!</b></Default>

c0000053
00:03:26.670 --> 00:03:29.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You need to get over it
and accept this reality, Nodoka.</b></Default>

c0000054
00:03:29.580 --> 00:03:32.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Nodoka Toyohama.
Wasn't she--</b></Default>

c0000055
00:03:32.670 --> 00:03:34.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Doka, tell us something
you like.</b></Default>

c0000056
00:03:34.460 --> 00:03:37.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Sure. I like Mai Sakurajima,
the actress.</b></Default>

c0000057
00:03:37.800 --> 00:03:40.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- From some idol group called
Sweet Palette or--</b></Default>

c0000058
00:03:40.300 --> 00:03:42.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Not Palette.
It's Bullet with a B.</b></Default>

c0000059
00:03:42.310 --> 00:03:43.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sweet Bullet!</b></Default>

c0000060
00:03:43.810 --> 00:03:46.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Anyway, how are
you two related, again?</b></Default>

c0000061
00:03:46.140 --> 00:03:48.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I told you before I have
a little sister.</b></Default>

c0000062
00:03:48.400 --> 00:03:50.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My dad got remarried when I
was young and they had her.</b></Default>

c0000063
00:03:50.770 --> 00:03:52.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's technically
my half sister.</b></Default>

c0000064
00:03:52.860 --> 00:03:55.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- But if she lives with them
then why is she here?</b></Default>

c0000065
00:03:55.320 --> 00:03:56.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Well, she showed up
at my doorstep out</b></Default>

c0000066
00:03:56.900 --> 00:03:58.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of the blue last night.</b></Default>

c0000067
00:03:58.240 --> 00:04:00.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She didn't wanna go home
so I let her sleep over,</b></Default>

c0000068
00:04:00.370 --> 00:04:02.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and when we woke up this morning
our bodies had been swapped.</b></Default>

c0000069
00:04:03.080 --> 00:04:04.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What is up with that?</b></Default>

c0000070
00:04:05.250 --> 00:04:07.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Toyohama, do you have
any idea why?</b></Default>

c0000071
00:04:07.580 --> 00:04:09.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Huh? Any idea why?</b></Default>

c0000072
00:04:09.540 --> 00:04:12.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Any clues as to why you ended
up swapping bodies with my Mai.</b></Default>

c0000073
00:04:12.670 --> 00:04:15.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Who's, "My Mai?"
- Ow, ow, ow, ow, ow, ow.</b></Default>

c0000074
00:04:15.760 --> 00:04:17.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I don't know anything!</b></Default>

c0000075
00:04:17.220 --> 00:04:18.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Like, I don't get it.</b></Default>

c0000076
00:04:18.260 --> 00:04:19.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How are you both staying
so ca--</b></Default>

c0000077
00:04:19.720 --> 00:04:21.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>how could you both stay calm?</b></Default>

c0000078
00:04:21.640 --> 00:04:24.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Talking minds transferring
between physical bodies,</b></Default>

c0000079
00:04:24.310 --> 00:04:26.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it's absolutely
positively bizarre!</b></Default>

c0000080
00:04:26.140 --> 00:04:27.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You're right.</b></Default>

c0000081
00:04:27.350 --> 00:04:29.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Is that all you have to say?</b></Default>

c0000082
00:04:29.230 --> 00:04:31.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Big si--Mai, are you fine
with this?</b></Default>

c0000083
00:04:31.860 --> 00:04:33.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is insane!
- Whether I'm okay</b></Default>

c0000084
00:04:33.860 --> 00:04:35.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with it or not,
we have to live with it.</b></Default>

c0000085
00:04:35.530 --> 00:04:36.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's already happened.</b></Default>

c0000086
00:04:36.860 --> 00:04:38.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Anyways, until we're back
to normal,</b></Default>

c0000087
00:04:38.900 --> 00:04:40.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll be living your life as you.</b></Default>

c0000088
00:04:40.610 --> 00:04:44.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So Nodoka, I need you
to live my life as me.</b></Default>

c0000089
00:04:44.740 --> 00:04:46.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thankfully this is all
I have lined up for work.</b></Default>

c0000090
00:04:46.950 --> 00:04:48.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A fashion magazine shoot,
a few interviews,</b></Default>

c0000091
00:04:48.910 --> 00:04:50.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and a commercial filming.</b></Default>

c0000092
00:04:50.750 --> 00:04:52.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That's surprisingly
little work for you.</b></Default>

c0000093
00:04:52.710 --> 00:04:54.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I cut back this term so</b></Default>

c0000094
00:04:54.420 --> 00:04:56.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a certain someone
wouldn't feel so lonely.</b></Default>

c0000095
00:04:56.550 --> 00:04:58.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- But if the ban on dating's
still in effect,</b></Default>

c0000096
00:04:58.300 --> 00:04:59.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>there's no real point.</b></Default>

c0000097
00:05:00.010 --> 00:05:01.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Nodoka, you've got
a full schedule.</b></Default>

c0000098
00:05:01.680 --> 00:05:03.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- But it's not real work.</b></Default>

c0000099
00:05:03.220 --> 00:05:05.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Most of these are just singing
and dance lessons.</b></Default>

c0000100
00:05:05.430 --> 00:05:07.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sweet Bullet has a solo gig at
the end of the month</b></Default>

c0000101
00:05:07.600 --> 00:05:08.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we're preparing for.</b></Default>

c0000102
00:05:08.890 --> 00:05:11.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hopefully we can
switch back before that.</b></Default>

c0000103
00:05:11.270 --> 00:05:13.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't have experience
with idol stuff so learning</b></Default>

c0000104
00:05:13.650 --> 00:05:14.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the routines might be tough.</b></Default>

c0000105
00:05:15.070 --> 00:05:17.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And what about you?
- Right.</b></Default>

c0000106
00:05:17.440 --> 00:05:19.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've done photo shoots
and interviews before</b></Default>

c0000107
00:05:19.530 --> 00:05:21.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I don't know about
the commercial.</b></Default>

c0000108
00:05:21.860 --> 00:05:23.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- The director for this
always sticks to the script</b></Default>

c0000109
00:05:23.990 --> 00:05:26.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so you'll be fine as long
as you prepare.</b></Default>

c0000110
00:05:26.540 --> 00:05:28.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, Sakuta, you can leave now.</b></Default>

c0000111
00:05:28.580 --> 00:05:30.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Huh? No way!</b></Default>

c0000112
00:05:30.330 --> 00:05:31.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's gonna happen
to my romantic</b></Default>

c0000113
00:05:31.670 --> 00:05:33.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>high school days with you?</b></Default>

c0000114
00:05:33.120 --> 00:05:35.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Let's meet up at 7:50
tomorrow morning, okay?</b></Default>

c0000115
00:05:35.670 --> 00:05:37.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'd like you to take Nodoka
to school for me.</b></Default>

c0000116
00:05:37.750 --> 00:05:39.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [groans]</b></Default>

c0000117
00:05:41.680 --> 00:05:43.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groaning]</b></Default>

c0000118
00:05:46.100 --> 00:05:47.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]
[cat grunts]</b></Default>

c0000119
00:05:48.560 --> 00:05:50.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]
Oh, no!</b></Default>

c0000120
00:05:50.140 --> 00:05:52.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nasuno and Hayate
were one step ahead!</b></Default>

c0000121
00:05:52.600 --> 00:05:54.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's supposed to be
the little sister's duty</b></Default>

c0000122
00:05:54.440 --> 00:05:55.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to wake up big brother.</b></Default>

c0000123
00:05:55.610 --> 00:05:57.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Morning, Kaede.</b></Default>

c0000124
00:05:58.020 --> 00:06:00.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Kaede wants to turn into
a cat, too.</b></Default>

c0000125
00:06:00.400 --> 00:06:02.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- And if my sister were
to somehow swap bodies</b></Default>

c0000126
00:06:02.450 --> 00:06:03.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with a cat...</b></Default>

c0000127
00:06:04.030 --> 00:06:05.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That would be
even more confusing.</b></Default>

c0000128
00:06:05.570 --> 00:06:07.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hmm?</b></Default>

c0000129
00:06:07.530 --> 00:06:10.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Um, I
should have asked
this earlier,</b></Default>

c0000130
00:06:10.370 --> 00:06:13.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but won't it be impossible
for me to pretend that I'm Mai?</b></Default>

c0000131
00:06:13.920 --> 00:06:16.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Anyone she's close with is gonna
be able to tell right away</b></Default>

c0000132
00:06:17.040 --> 00:06:18.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>something's off.
- Oh, don't worry.</b></Default>

c0000133
00:06:19.050 --> 00:06:20.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mai doesn't have friends
so you're fine.</b></Default>

c0000134
00:06:20.840 --> 00:06:22.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Huh?
- Oh, yeah?</b></Default>

c0000135
00:06:22.340 --> 00:06:24.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't act like you're not in
the same boat.</b></Default>

c0000136
00:06:24.090 --> 00:06:26.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hey, hold on a minute.
I have friends.</b></Default>

c0000137
00:06:26.090 --> 00:06:27.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A whole three.</b></Default>

c0000138
00:06:27.220 --> 00:06:29.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Anyway, you get the idea.</b></Default>

c0000139
00:06:29.140 --> 00:06:30.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Pretending to be me while
at school's gonna be</b></Default>

c0000140
00:06:30.970 --> 00:06:32.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a piece of cake.
- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000141
00:06:34.020 --> 00:06:37.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Sit quietly during classes
and go home right after.</b></Default>

c0000142
00:06:37.230 --> 00:06:38.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's no real reason
to talk to anyone.</b></Default>

c0000143
00:06:38.900 --> 00:06:40.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- O--okay.</b></Default>

c0000144
00:06:40.570 --> 00:06:43.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, uh, it's the same for me.
- Huh?</b></Default>

c0000145
00:06:43.610 --> 00:06:46.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Last year when my debut
was set I lost any free time</b></Default>

c0000146
00:06:46.660 --> 00:06:48.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I had to hang out
with my friends from school.</b></Default>

c0000147
00:06:48.780 --> 00:06:50.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- The story of two
friendless sisters.</b></Default>

c0000148
00:06:51.040 --> 00:06:52.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're going to make me cry.</b></Default>

c0000149
00:06:52.700 --> 00:06:55.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Well, then, I'm gonna head off
to Nodoka's school from here.</b></Default>

c0000150
00:06:55.870 --> 00:06:58.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It's some rich girls' school
over in Yokohama, right?</b></Default>

c0000151
00:06:58.750 --> 00:07:01.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- So I think I have an idea
why this happened with Nodoka.</b></Default>

c0000152
00:07:01.670 --> 00:07:03.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But do you think you could
poke her about it?</b></Default>

c0000153
00:07:03.420 --> 00:07:05.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm pretty sure
it's because of me.</b></Default>

c0000154
00:07:05.760 --> 00:07:07.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It must be rough having
a big sister</b></Default>

c0000155
00:07:07.760 --> 00:07:09.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that everyone in
the country knows about.</b></Default>

c0000156
00:07:10.140 --> 00:07:13.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- There's that but also
the rivalry between our mothers.</b></Default>

c0000157
00:07:13.270 --> 00:07:14.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hmm?</b></Default>

c0000158
00:07:14.480 --> 00:07:16.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Have I never mentioned
this before?</b></Default>

c0000159
