00:13:24.470 --> 00:13:25.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Come on.</b></Default>

c0000321
00:13:25.720 --> 00:13:26.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Well, 'cause you brought yet</b></Default>

c0000322
00:13:26.720 --> 00:13:28.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>another new girl home with you.</b></Default>

c0000323
00:13:28.470 --> 00:13:30.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- She happens to be Mai's
little sister,</b></Default>

c0000324
00:13:30.600 --> 00:13:32.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and she's going to be staying
with us for a little while.</b></Default>

c0000325
00:13:32.730 --> 00:13:33.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Nice to meet you!</b></Default>

c0000326
00:13:33.980 --> 00:13:36.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm Nodoka Toyohama.
[laughs]</b></Default>

c0000327
00:13:36.650 --> 00:13:39.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crickets chirping]</b></Default>

c0000328
00:13:40.110 --> 00:13:41.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [exhales]</b></Default>

c0000329
00:13:43.820 --> 00:13:47.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In the future if Mai and I were
to get married then...</b></Default>

c0000330
00:13:47.990 --> 00:13:50.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nodoka Toyohama would be
my little sister.</b></Default>

c0000331
00:13:50.830 --> 00:13:53.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I mean, sister-in-law?
No, wait.</b></Default>

c0000332
00:13:53.880 --> 00:13:56.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They're half-sisters so maybe
half-sister-in-law?</b></Default>

c0000333
00:13:56.670 --> 00:13:58.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm lost.</b></Default>

c0000334
00:13:59.130 --> 00:14:01.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What would be the right way
to address her?</b></Default>

c0000335
00:14:02.880 --> 00:14:04.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You sure took your sweet time
in there.</b></Default>

c0000336
00:14:04.840 --> 00:14:06.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Were you thinking about me
or something?</b></Default>

c0000337
00:14:06.890 --> 00:14:08.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Well obviously.</b></Default>

c0000338
00:14:08.100 --> 00:14:09.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm always thinking about you,
Mai.</b></Default>

c0000339
00:14:09.600 --> 00:14:10.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yeah, yeah.</b></Default>

c0000340
00:14:10.890 --> 00:14:12.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- To be honest, I
was actually pretending</b></Default>

c0000341
00:14:12.890 --> 00:14:14.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to be a submarine.</b></Default>

c0000342
00:14:14.270 --> 00:14:15.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]
- Hold on.</b></Default>

c0000343
00:14:16.360 --> 00:14:17.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Have you never played that game?</b></Default>

c0000344
00:14:19.530 --> 00:14:21.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Your scars.
They're still there.</b></Default>

c0000345
00:14:23.110 --> 00:14:24.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You wanna touch 'em?
- Why would I?</b></Default>

c0000346
00:14:25.030 --> 00:14:27.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Because it would make me happy
if you did.</b></Default>

c0000347
00:14:27.330 --> 00:14:29.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Stop being weird
and go put some clothes on.</b></Default>

c0000348
00:14:29.830 --> 00:14:31.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It would be a problem
if your naked body got burned</b></Default>

c0000349
00:14:31.830 --> 00:14:33.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>into Nodoka's memory.</b></Default>

c0000350
00:14:33.580 --> 00:14:35.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- She's not a little kid,
you know.</b></Default>

c0000351
00:14:35.330 --> 00:14:37.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- No, she totally is.</b></Default>

c0000352
00:14:37.130 --> 00:14:39.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- And who was it who just
got into a giant argument</b></Default>

c0000353
00:14:39.380 --> 00:14:40.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with that little kid?</b></Default>

c0000354
00:14:40.920 --> 00:14:42.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Well, that's--</b></Default>

c0000355
00:14:42.510 --> 00:14:45.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I think it's best to be honest
through this situation.</b></Default>

c0000356
00:14:45.340 --> 00:14:46.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I don't wanna hear
sound logic.</b></Default>

c0000357
00:14:47.050 --> 00:14:48.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]</b></Default>

c0000358
00:14:48.300 --> 00:14:51.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[melancholic music]</b></Default>

c0000359
00:14:51.270 --> 00:14:58.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

c0000360
00:15:20.710 --> 00:15:27.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

c0000361
00:15:35.020 --> 00:15:36.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Have you been a good kitty,
Hayate?</b></Default>

c0000362
00:15:37.600 --> 00:15:39.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[cat grumbles]
[giggles]</b></Default>

c0000363
00:15:40.400 --> 00:15:41.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hey, Makinohara.</b></Default>

c0000364
00:15:41.980 --> 00:15:43.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You don't have a big sister,
right?</b></Default>

c0000365
00:15:44.070 --> 00:15:45.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Right.
I'm an only child.</b></Default>

c0000366
00:15:46.450 --> 00:15:48.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But sometimes I wish I had
a sibling.</b></Default>

c0000367
00:15:48.610 --> 00:15:51.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A wonderful big sis
would be nice.</b></Default>

c0000368
00:15:51.280 --> 00:15:54.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Kaede would also be happy
to have a wonderful big sister.</b></Default>

c0000369
00:15:54.620 --> 00:15:56.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But only older than big brother,
though.</b></Default>

c0000370
00:15:56.290 --> 00:15:57.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[cat meows]</b></Default>

c0000371
00:15:57.370 --> 00:15:58.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Kaede must remain
the only</b></Default>

c0000372
00:15:58.960 --> 00:15:59.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>little sister to him.</b></Default>

c0000373
00:16:00.000 --> 00:16:01.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [chuckles nervously]</b></Default>

c0000374
00:16:03.130 --> 00:16:05.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[camera shutter clicking]</b></Default>

c0000375
00:16:06.420 --> 00:16:07.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're working on
that commercial</b></Default>

c0000376
00:16:07.680 --> 00:16:09.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>tomorrow morning, right?</b></Default>

c0000377
00:16:09.340 --> 00:16:11.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What do you think
about smiling like this?</b></Default>

c0000378
00:16:11.350 --> 00:16:13.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Wouldn't it be better
to get Mai's opinion</b></Default>

c0000379
00:16:13.220 --> 00:16:14.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>on stuff like that?</b></Default>

c0000380
00:16:14.560 --> 00:16:16.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- We're not talking
about her right now.</b></Default>

c0000381
00:16:16.560 --> 00:16:19.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You do you but it's too much
for an amateur like me.</b></Default>

c0000382
00:16:19.400 --> 00:16:21.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Then I won't ask again.</b></Default>

c0000383
00:16:22.270 --> 00:16:24.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Ah, good morning, Sakuta.</b></Default>

c0000384
00:16:25.570 --> 00:16:27.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Oh, hey.
Is that Mai?</b></Default>

c0000385
00:16:27.900 --> 00:16:29.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- No, you can't have this.</b></Default>

c0000386
00:16:29.660 --> 00:16:31.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I haven't finished reading
it yet!</b></Default>

c0000387
00:16:31.780 --> 00:16:34.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've got studying to do.
- Okay.</b></Default>

c0000388
00:16:34.290 --> 00:16:36.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll just go and look at
the real deal.</b></Default>

c0000389
00:16:36.200 --> 00:16:38.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Sakuta.
- Hmm?</b></Default>

c0000390
00:16:38.580 --> 00:16:41.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What you just said
really gave me the ick.</b></Default>

c0000391
00:16:43.670 --> 00:16:45.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[doorbell chiming]
- Hi, welcome.</b></Default>

c0000392
00:16:45.090 --> 00:16:46.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[stammers]</b></Default>

c0000393
00:16:48.880 --> 00:16:49.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mai.</b></Default>

c0000394
00:16:50.050 --> 00:16:51.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's wrong?</b></Default>

c0000395
00:16:51.550 --> 00:16:53.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I have my singing
practice soon</b></Default>

c0000396
00:16:53.220 --> 00:16:54.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so I thought I should
eat something first</b></Default>

c0000397
00:16:54.680 --> 00:16:56.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>because I'll get hungry.</b></Default>

c0000398
00:16:56.470 --> 00:16:57.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[cell phone vibrates]
[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000399
00:16:57.850 --> 00:17:00.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Is that Toyohama's smartphone?</b></Default>

c0000400
00:17:00.650 --> 00:17:02.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yeah, it's another text
from Nodoka's mother.</b></Default>

c0000401
00:17:02.980 --> 00:17:06.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've gotten about 50 more
of them since this morning.</b></Default>

c0000402
00:17:07.940 --> 00:17:08.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[exhales sharply]</b></Default>

c0000403
00:17:09.990 --> 00:17:11.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>One of these, please.</b></Default>

c0000404
00:17:11.320 --> 00:17:13.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Spaghetti with a tomato sauce,
right?</b></Default>

c0000405
00:17:14.450 --> 00:17:16.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's been preparing
for the commercial shoot</b></Default>

c0000406
00:17:16.700 --> 00:17:19.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to the point of rehearsing what
facial expressions to make.</b></Default>

c0000407
00:17:19.540 --> 00:17:21.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What's this so suddenly?</b></Default>

c0000408
00:17:21.540 --> 00:17:23.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I thought hearing about that
might have been the real reason</b></Default>

c0000409
00:17:23.880 --> 00:17:25.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you came by.
- It was because I wanted</b></Default>

c0000410
00:17:25.710 --> 00:17:27.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to see my boyfriend's face,
actually.</b></Default>

c0000411
00:17:27.590 --> 00:17:29.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That makes me so happy.</b></Default>

c0000412
00:17:29.220 --> 00:17:31.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Show me some
genuine happiness.</b></Default>

c0000413
00:17:31.720 --> 00:17:33.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- If you have any advice,
I'll pass it onto her.</b></Default>

c0000414
00:17:33.840 --> 00:17:36.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Did Nodoka say
she wanted some?</b></Default>

c0000415
00:17:36.180 --> 00:17:38.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- No.
- Then I've got nothing.</b></Default>

c0000416
00:17:38.310 --> 00:17:39.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- So she was on your mind
after all.</b></Default>

c0000417
00:17:41.020 --> 00:17:42.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- She'll be fine.</b></Default>

c0000418
00:17:42.230 --> 00:17:43.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If she remembers
what she learned</b></Default>

c0000419
00:17:43.690 --> 00:17:44.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>from her theater training,</b></Default>

c0000420
00:17:44.980 --> 00:17:46.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>there won't be any issues.</b></Default>

c0000421
00:17:47.020 --> 00:17:49.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[birds chirping]</b></Default>

c0000422
00:17:53.030 --> 00:17:55.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

c0000423
00:17:57.950 --> 00:18:00.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [yawns]</b></Default>

c0000424
00:18:00.290 --> 00:18:02.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They really start early in
the morning. I'm exhausted.</b></Default>

c0000425
00:18:02.710 --> 00:18:04.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Miss Mai Sakurajima
is on set.</b></Default>

c0000426
00:18:05.960 --> 00:18:07.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[all speaking at once]</b></Default>

c0000427
00:18:07.420 --> 00:18:08.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Thank you all
for your hard work.</b></Default>

c0000428
00:18:09.460 --> 00:18:10.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000429
00:18:10.970 --> 00:18:12.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Let's get the camera
test started.</b></Default>

c0000430
00:18:12.680 --> 00:18:13.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Before the train comes in.</b></Default>

c0000431
00:18:15.850 --> 00:18:17.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- All right, rolling.</b></Default>

c0000432
00:18:17.180 --> 00:18:18.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And...</b></Default>

c0000433
00:18:19.350 --> 00:18:20.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Action!</b></Default>

c0000434
00:18:22.600 --> 00:18:24.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]
- Okay, cut!</b></Default>

c0000435
00:18:24.600 --> 00:18:27.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

c0000436
00:18:29.110 --> 00:18:30.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [groans]</b></Default>

c0000437
00:18:31.190 --> 00:18:33.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- After a train passes,
we'll start the actual filming.</b></Default>

c0000438
00:18:36.030 --> 00:18:37.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[train brakes hissing]</b></Default>

c0000439
00:18:37.740 --> 00:18:39.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [whimpering]</b></Default>

c0000440
00:18:42.040 --> 00:18:45.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[breathing heavily]</b></Default>

c0000441
00:18:47.000 --> 00:18:49.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[labored breathing]</b></Default>

c0000442
00:18:49.630 --> 00:18:51.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Is she okay?
She seems off.</b></Default>

c0000443
00:18:51.880 --> 00:18:54.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- All right, starting takes.
- Take one!</b></Default>

c0000444
00:18:54.220 --> 00:18:55.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Take one!</b></Default>

c0000445
00:18:55.510 --> 00:18:58.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [labored breathing]</b></Default>

c0000446
00:18:59.390 --> 00:19:01.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]
all: Huh?</b></Default>

c0000447
00:19:01.140 --> 00:19:04.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [panicked breathing]</b></Default>

c0000448
00:19:06.850 --> 00:19:07.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

c0000449
00:19:08.060 --> 00:19:10.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Stop the cameras!
- Mai? Mai?</b></Default>

c0000450
00:19:10.650 --> 00:19:13.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Stay calm.
Just take slow, deep breaths.</b></Default>

c0000451
00:19:13.530 --> 00:19:16.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

c0000452
00:19:16.530 --> 00:19:19.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[cicadas chirping]</b></Default>

c0000453
00:19:19.990 --> 00:19:21.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Sakuta.</b></Default>

c0000454
00:19:21.990 --> 00:19:23.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You're doing another
morning run?</b></Default>

c0000455
00:19:24.040 --> 00:19:26.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'm getting my stamina up
for the concert.</b></Default>

c0000456
00:19:26.170 --> 00:19:28.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, how did the filming go?</b></Default>

c0000457
00:19:28.460 --> 00:19:30.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Please observe
the depressed look on my face.</b></Default>

c0000458
00:19:31.000 --> 00:19:33.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I can tell that
it didn't go perfect,</b></Default>

c0000459
00:19:33.130 --> 00:19:35.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but they must have finished
it after a few retakes, right?</b></Default>

c0000460
00:19:35.720 --> 00:19:38.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- No, she didn't even make
it that far.</b></Default>

c0000461
00:19:38.340 --> 00:19:40.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She got dizzy before
the first take</b></Default>

c0000462
00:19:40.100 --> 00:19:41.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and she collapsed.
- Huh?</b></Default>

c0000463
00:19:41.850 --> 00:19:44.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- They canceled the shoot before
it started.</b></Default>

c0000464
00:19:44.180 --> 00:19:47.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The staff was saying that she
probably just hyperventilated.</b></Default>

c0000465
00:19:47.270 --> 00:19:50.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- But why would that--
- When it came down to it,</b></Default>

c0000466
00:19:50.230 --> 00:19:51.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it was too much--</b></Default>

c0000467
00:19:51.940 --> 00:19:54.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the crushing weight of the trust
and expectations people have</b></Default>

c0000468
00:19:54.400 --> 00:19:56.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for Mai Sakurajima.
- [groans]</b></Default>

c0000469
00:19:56.950 --> 00:19:58.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You don't get it?</b></Default>

c0000470
00:19:59.280 --> 00:20:01.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All of your accomplishments
have felt like pressure on her</b></Default>

c0000471
00:20:01.580 --> 00:20:03.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>this whole time.
I'm sure of it.</b></Default>

c0000472
00:20:04.450 --> 00:20:07.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[school bell ringing]</b></Default>

c0000473
00:20:07.500 --> 00:20:09.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Well, someone's in a bad mood.</b></Default>

c0000474
00:20:09.170 --> 00:20:10.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is something wrong?</b></Default>

c0000475
00:20:10.670 --> 00:20:12.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'm fine.</b></Default>

c0000476
00:20:12.210 --> 00:20:14.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was just thinking about
how I might feel if I had</b></Default>

c0000477
00:20:14.920 --> 00:20:17.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>an awesome big sister that
was amazing at everything.</b></Default>

c0000478
00:20:17.510 --> 00:20:19.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Okay, why?</b></Default>

c0000479
00:20:19.140 --> 00:20:20.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I've never had any experience
being compared</b></Default>

c0000480
00:20:21.010 --> 00:20:22.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to a big sister, so--</b></Default>

c0000481
00:20:22.810 --> 00:20:25.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Then how about asking someone
who has a big sister like that?</b></Default>

c0000482
00:20:26.060 --> 00:20:26.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Huh?</b></Default>

c0000483
00:20:28.020 --> 00:20:29.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [groans]</b></Default>

c0000484
00:20:29.400 --> 00:20:30.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000485
00:20:30.730 --> 00:20:31.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000486
00:20:32.270 --> 00:20:33.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groans]</b></Default>

c0000487
00:20:33.650 --> 00:20:34.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[scoffs]</b></Default>

c0000488
00:20:34.940 --> 00:20:35.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What is it?</b></Default>

c0000489
00:20:36.030 --> 00:20:37.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Sakuta here has a question</b></Default>

c0000490
00:20:37.320 --> 00:20:38.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to ask you.</b></Default>

c0000491
00:20:38.610 --> 00:20:40.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Do you have an older sister,
Kamisato?</b></Default>

c0000492
00:20:40.990 --> 00:20:43.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I do, yes. Wait.</b></Default>

c0000493
00:20:43.120 --> 00:20:44.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But how do you not know
about her?</b></Default>

c0000494
00:20:44.910 --> 00:20:47.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- And remind me again why
I'm supposed to know about all</b></Default>

c0000495
00:20:47.620 --> 00:20:49.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of your family affairs?
- You aren't.</b></Default>

c0000496
00:20:49.620 --> 00:20:51.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But she went here
till last year.</b></Default>

c0000497
00:20:51.630 --> 00:20:53.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She was student
council president.</b></Default>

c0000498
00:20:53.420 --> 00:20:55.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You've seen her.
- Doesn't ring a bell.</b></Default>

c0000499
00:20:55.550 --> 00:20:58.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Can I go now?
- Just a little more, please.</b></Default>

c0000500
00:20:58.670 --> 00:21:00.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Your sister was brilliant,
then.</b></Default>

c0000501
00:21:00.630 --> 00:21:03.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- She got into the best
national university in Japan</b></Default>

c0000502
00:21:03.220 --> 00:21:04.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>her first year trying.</b></Default>

c0000503
00:21:04.680 --> 00:21:06.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- And would you say you like
your big sister?</b></Default>

c0000504
00:21:06.970 --> 00:21:08.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Not really.</b></Default>

c0000505
00:21:08.100 --> 00:21:09.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Then, do you hate her?</b></Default>

c0000506
00:21:09.230 --> 00:21:10.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Not really.</b></Default>

c0000507
00:21:10.390 --> 00:21:12.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I see.
I get it now.</b></Default>

c0000508
00:21:12.350 --> 00:21:15.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Get what?
What are you going on about now?</b></Default>

c0000509
00:21:15.110 --> 00:21:16.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It's not like or hate.</b></Default>

c0000510
00:21:16.900 --> 00:21:18.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This kind of relationship's</b></Default>

c0000511
00:21:18.190 --> 00:21:20.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>way more complex
than I imagined.</b></Default>

c0000512
00:21:20.990 --> 00:21:23.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It's not like I actually
hate her.</b></Default>

c0000513
00:21:23.410 --> 00:21:26.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But it's also annoying when
my mom is constantly telling me</b></Default>

c0000514
00:21:26.660 --> 00:21:28.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to follow my sister's example
and study more.</b></Default>

c0000515
00:21:29.460 --> 00:21:32.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[birds chirping]</b></Default>

c0000516
00:21:33.830 --> 00:21:35.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [exhales]</b></Default>

c0000517
00:21:38.130 --> 00:21:39.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000518
00:21:39.510 --> 00:21:40.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mai, hey.</b></Default>

c0000519
00:21:41.090 --> 00:21:42.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Here. Take this.</b></Default>

c0000520
00:21:42.680 --> 00:21:43.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's to my place.</b></Default>

c0000521
00:21:43.970 --> 00:21:45.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You're giving me a spare key?</b></Default>

c0000522
00:21:45.720 --> 00:21:48.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I wouldn't give something
that important away so easily!</b></Default>

c0000523
00:21:48.310 --> 00:21:49.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't be gross!
- That hurts!</b></Default>

c0000524
00:21:49.770 --> 00:21:51.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'm only lending it to you.</b></Default>

c0000525
00:21:51.310 --> 00:21:52.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm really counting on you.</b></Default>

c0000526
00:21:53.440 --> 00:21:54.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- If you're still worried,</b></Default>

c0000527
00:21:54.440 --> 00:21:55.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you really should just go</b></Default>

c0000528
00:21:55.520 --> 00:21:57.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and talk to her yourself,
though.</b></Default>

c0000529
00:21:58.030 --> 00:22:00.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I have zero idea what
I'd even say to her.</b></Default>

c0000530
00:22:00.320 --> 00:22:01.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You can start with that.</b></Default>

c0000531
00:22:01.530 --> 00:22:02.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just be honest with her.</b></Default>

c0000532
00:22:02.740 --> 00:22:03.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Don't want to.</b></Default>

c0000533
00:22:04.410 --> 00:22:06.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yeah, guess you still have
to save face being</b></Default>

c0000534
00:22:06.780 --> 00:22:08.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the big sister and all, right?</b></Default>

c0000535
00:22:08.870 --> 00:22:10.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, I'll head over now,
then.</b></Default>

c0000536
00:22:11.040 --> 00:22:12.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hold on.
- What is it?</b></Default>

c0000537
00:22:14.750 --> 00:22:17.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Never open the cabinets in
the Japanese-style room.</b></Default>

c0000538
00:22:17.920 --> 00:22:19.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Never, no matter what?</b></Default>

c0000539
00:22:26.600 --> 00:22:28.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No matter what. Huh.</b></Default>

c0000540
00:22:31.850 --> 00:22:34.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chiming]</b></Default>

c0000541
00:22:34.600 --> 00:22:36.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yes?
- It's Azusagawa.</b></Default>

c0000542
00:22:36.770 --> 00:22:37.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What?</b></Default>

c0000543
00:22:38.020 --> 00:22:39.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Can I come up?</b></Default>

c0000544
00:22:41.440 --> 00:22:43.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Of course if you say no
then I'll just use</b></Default>

c0000545
00:22:43.320 --> 00:22:45.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the spare key I got from Mai.</b></Default>

c0000546
00:22:46.910 --> 00:22:50.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- So, uh, did my sister
say anything to you?</b></Default>

c0000547
00:22:50.200 --> 00:22:51.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Not much.</b></Default>

c0000548
00:22:51.700 --> 00:22:53.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She wasn't too concerned about
the gig.</b></Default>

c0000549
00:22:53.910 --> 00:22:55.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I mean, she assumed you would
end up having quite</b></Default>

c0000550
00:22:55.670 --> 00:22:57.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a few outtakes.</b></Default>

c0000551
00:22:57.250 --> 00:22:59.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But still she had no doubt
you'd be able to get</b></Default>

c0000552
00:22:59.090 --> 00:23:00.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a passing grade
from that director.</b></Default>

c0000553
00:23:00.630 --> 00:23:02.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You mean it?</b></Default>

c0000554
00:23:02.090 --> 00:23:03.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hey, you know,</b></Default>

c0000555
00:23:03.760 --> 00:23:05.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>wouldn't it be best
if you just smiled like that?</b></Default>

c0000556
00:23:05.890 --> 00:23:08.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Huh?
- For the commercial shoot.</b></Default>

c0000557
00:23:08.180 --> 00:23:09.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When you were practicing
you were forcing yourself</b></Default>

c0000558
00:23:10.060 --> 00:23:11.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to smile like Mai would.</b></Default>

c0000559
00:23:11.600 --> 00:23:13.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But honestly,
it wasn't believable.</b></Default>

c0000560
00:23:13.520 --> 00:23:14.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]</b></Default>

c0000561
00:23:15.270 --> 00:23:16.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Well, anyway...</b></Default>

c0000562
00:23:17.400 --> 00:23:19.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is a crime scene.</b></Default>

c0000563
00:23:20.150 --> 00:23:21.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This can't be
the real reason she gave me</b></Default>

c0000564
00:23:21.820 --> 00:23:23.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the spare key, right?</b></Default>

c0000565
00:23:23.570 --> 00:23:25.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]
Have you had anything to eat?</b></Default>

c0000566
00:23:25.700 --> 00:23:27.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Not since this morning, no.</b></Default>

c0000567
00:23:27.450 --> 00:23:29.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Then I'll make you something.</b></Default>

c0000568
00:23:29.160 --> 00:23:31.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So you can go freshen up with
a bath first.</b></Default>

c0000569
00:23:31.740 --> 00:23:33.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Don't you dare peek.</b></Default>

c0000570
00:23:33.120 --> 00:23:34.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Does that mean you're asking
me to?</b></Default>

c0000571
00:23:34.620 --> 00:23:36.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Of course not, weirdo! Die!</b></Default>

c0000572
00:23:41.460 --> 00:23:42.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[exhales]</b></Default>

c0000573
00:23:50.890 --> 00:23:52.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [exhales]</b></Default>

c0000574
00:23:55.680 --> 00:23:58.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [singing in Japanese]</b></Default>

c0000575
00:23:58.730 --> 00:24:01.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>["Fukashigi no Carte" plays]</b></Default>

c0000576
00:24:01.650 --> 00:24:08.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

c0000577
00:24:47.360 --> 00:24:54.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

c0000578
00:24:55.950 --> 00:25:00.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>all: Oh, Sakuta.
You're such a rascal.</b></Default>

